# Docker Assignment: Node.js Website

### Docker Build Command
docker build -t my-node-app:latest .

### Docker Run Command
docker run -d -P --name assignment-container my-node-app:latest

### How to display the website
1. Run `docker ps` to find the public port assigned by Docker.
2. Open a browser and navigate to `http://localhost:[PORT_NUMBER]` 
   (e.g., http://localhost:32768).